## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on secondary sources, which may not provide the most current research findings. Additionally, the interpretations of these theories can vary, and the practical applications may differ across educational settings. Further empirical research is needed to validate the effectiveness of these theories in contemporary educational practices.